column2: I enjoy being around old people.
column3: I fear that when I am old all of my friends will be gone.
column4: I like to go visit my older relatives.
column5: I have never lied about my age in order to appear younger.
column6: I fear it will be very hard for me to find contentment in old age.
column7: The older I become, the more I worry about my health.
column8: I will have plenty to occupy my time when I am old.
column9: I get nervous when I think about someone else making decisions for me when I am old.
column10: It doesn't bother me at all to imagine myself as being old.
column11: I enjoy talking with old people.
column12: I expect to feel good about life when I am old.
column13: I have never dreaded the day I would look in the mirror and see gray hairs.
column14: I feel very comfortable when I am around an old person.
column15: I worry that people will ignore me when I am old.
column16: I have never dreaded looking old.
column17: I believe that I will still be able to do most things for myself when I am old.
column18: I am afraid that there will be no meaning in life when I am old.
column19: I expect to feel good about myself when I am old.
column20: I enjoy doing things for old people.
